Titolo: Pop Idol (video game)

Anno: 2003

Descrizione: Pop Idol (American Idol in North America) is a rhythm video game developed by Hothouse Creations and published by Codemasters for PlayStation 2, Microsoft Windows and Game Boy Advance. It is based on the reality talent show franchise Idol. The American version uses footage from the second season.



Genere: rhythm 

Valutazione: N/A
